  Methods

· getAliasType

Summary  |  Top 
   public int getAliasType()

Returns one of the constants defined in DiskAlias.java: ALIAS_VOL, etc. Returns ALIAS_NOLONGER if this object no longer exists, or if an error occurs. The alias will be resolved without user interaction, and the alias will not be modified.
